dct_title_s: Moyen-orient : essai de carte économique / Présidence du Conseil, Secretariat général du gouvernement, Direction de la documentation.
dct_description_sm: Relief show by spot heights, Shows railways, pipelines,  cultural zones, mineral resources,industries location, historical names are given, archaeological sites are located. "Presidence du Conseil Direction de la Documentation." Ancillary map: Les pétroles du Moyen orient. Shows oil wells and pipelines. Gas concessions granted to companies are shown by color code. Ancillary map:  [Israel, western Syria, and Jordan]. Scale 1:1,5000,000. Shows location of  major industries. In upper right margin: "Carte no. 79." On verso: "Carte no. 77". "Reproduction interdite." T.4.444."
